%% Staff Management — invite, roles, capabilities, schedules, suspend/remove
%% Permission model:
%%   Owner  — manage everyone; invite Admin/Staff; change roles; transfer ownership; remove anyone.
%%   Admin  — manage Staff only; cannot manage other Admins or the Owner.
%%   Staff  — view-only; can see own profile + schedule.
%% Invite acceptance is handled in dashboard-access.mmd. Schedules feed the availability engine in booking-management.mmd.
flowchart TD
    Start([Open Staff]) --> List[Staff list<br/>name, role, status, services]
    List --> Action{Choose action}

    %% --- View own profile is open to all roles ---
    Action -->|Open staff member| Profile[Staff profile<br/>role, capabilities, schedule, status]

    %% --- Write actions gate by role + target ---
    Action -->|Invite| CanInvite{Role = Owner/Admin?}
    CanInvite -->|No| Denied[Action not permitted] --> List
    Profile -->|Edit / Suspend / Remove / Change role| Scope{Actor allowed on this target?}
    Scope -->|Admin acting on Admin/Owner| Denied
    Scope -->|Allowed| EditAction{Which action?}

    %% --- Invite ---
    CanInvite -->|Yes| InviteForm[Invite form<br/>email + role + services they can perform]
    InviteForm --> RoleAllowed{Inviting role actor may grant?<br/>Admin can invite Staff only}
    RoleAllowed -->|No| Denied
    RoleAllowed -->|Yes| SendInvite[(Create pending invite)]
    SendInvite --> EmailInvite[/Email invite link — accepted in dashboard-access.mmd/]
    EmailInvite --> List

    %% --- Pending invite management ---
    Action -->|Open pending invite| PendingInvite[Pending invite]
    PendingInvite --> InviteOps{Resend or revoke?}
    InviteOps -->|Resend| ResendInvite[/Re-send invite link/] --> List
    InviteOps -->|Revoke| RevokeInvite[(Revoke invite)] --> List

    %% --- Edit profile / capabilities ---
    EditAction -->|Edit| EditForm[Edit profile + role + capabilities<br/>services they can perform]
    EditForm --> SaveEdit[(Save changes)] --> Profile

    %% --- Change role ---
    EditAction -->|Change role| RoleChange[Set role: Admin / Staff]
    RoleChange --> SaveRole[(Update role)] --> Profile

    %% --- Manage schedule / time off (feeds availability engine) ---
    Action -->|Manage schedule| CanSched{Role = Owner/Admin?}
    CanSched -->|No| Denied
    CanSched -->|Yes| Schedule[Set per-staff working hours,<br/>breaks, time off] --> SaveSched[(Save schedule)] --> List

    %% --- Suspend / reactivate (drives Suspended gate in dashboard-access.mmd) ---
    EditAction -->|Suspend| Suspend[(Set status = Suspended)]
    Suspend --> FutureSusp{Has future bookings?}
    FutureSusp -->|Yes| ReassignSusp[Reassign or cancel upcoming bookings]
    FutureSusp -->|No| DoneSusp[Access revoked on next login]
    ReassignSusp --> DoneSusp --> Profile
    Profile -->|Reactivate| Reactivate[(Set status = Active)] --> Profile

    %% --- Remove staff ---
    EditAction -->|Remove| RemoveConfirm{Confirm remove?}
    RemoveConfirm -->|No| Profile
    RemoveConfirm -->|Yes| FutureRem{Has future bookings?}
    FutureRem -->|Yes| ReassignRem[Reassign bookings to other<br/>capable staff, or cancel]
    FutureRem -->|No| DoRemove
    ReassignRem --> DoRemove[(Deactivate + revoke access,<br/>retain past records)] --> List

    %% --- Transfer ownership (Owner only) ---
    Action -->|Transfer ownership| IsOwner{Role = Owner?}
    IsOwner -->|No| Denied
    IsOwner -->|Yes| PickNewOwner[Select an Admin as new Owner]
    PickNewOwner --> ConfirmXfer{Confirm transfer?}
    ConfirmXfer -->|No| List
    ConfirmXfer -->|Yes| DoXfer[(Promote target to Owner,<br/>demote self to Admin)] --> List
